N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 8 ยง 560.1 - Applicability of this part

State Regulations

This Part shall govern vehicular and pedestrian traffic
and parking upon the highways, streets, roads and sidewalks owned, controlled
or maintained by State University of New York, and shall apply to students, faculty, employees, visitors and all other persons upon such
premises. Notes
